          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">🏙️ Nashville Service</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">⚡ Same-Day Available</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">🛡️ Insured & Bonded</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">📸 Post-Clean Photos</span>
        </div>

