          <li>What guests notice and complain about</li>
          <li>How to stage for photos</li>
          <li>Inventory and restocking needs</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Reliability</h3>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          A no-show on turnover day is a disaster. You need a company that:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600">
          <li>Shows up when scheduled, every time</li>
          <li>Has backup staff for emergencies</li>
          <li>Communicates immediately if anything goes wrong</li>
          <li>Handles last-minute schedule changes</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Communication Systems</h3>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Professional STR cleaners should:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600">
          <li>Confirm when they're heading to your property</li>
          <li>Alert you when cleaning is complete</li>
          <li>Report any damage or issues found</li>
          <li>Send photos of the completed clean</li>
          <li>Flag low supplies before they run out</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Insurance and Professionalism</h3>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          They're accessing your property regularly. You need:
        </p>

